Bad hair days are inevitable for women. They signal a date to the salon, however, due to unforeseen circumstances, this may not be possible. If you do not have time to get mini twists done or do them yourself, you can opt for natural hair cornrows but if time does not allow, you can opt to tie turbans. A turban can be styled differently and it comes in different colours depending on your liking and outfit of the day. First, you will need a head scarf. Ensure you buy one that compliments your skin tone and will match your outfits. Have a variety of colours for options. How to tie your turban